          Ideum Drafting Tables include an Intel&reg; Quad Core i7 computer with 16GB RAM, 500GB Solid State Drive, and an NVIDIA Graphics Card.
        </p>
      </li>
      
      <li class="client-slide" ng-class="{active: clientSliderIndex==0}">
        <div class="svgHolder">
          {% include '/images/products/svg/reach.svg' %}
        </div>
