        <p>
          Along with 60 touch points, the 3M™ projected-capacitive touch system on the Drafting Tables has palm rejection and an anti-stiction strengthen surface.
        </p>
      </li>

      <li class="client-slide" ng-class="{active: clientSliderIndex==0}">
