        <p>
          The Drafting Multitouch Table is ruggedized and easy to set up making it perfect for trade shows, traveling exhibits and special events. You can purchase the table with an optional ATA flight case. You can also rent the Drafting Table 46 and Drafting Table 55 models directly from Ideum.
        </p>
      </li>

      <li class="client-slide" ng-class="{active: clientSliderIndex==0}">
        <div class="svgHolder">
          {% include '/images/products/svg/warranty.svg' %}
        </div>
